Trade/Device Name(s): Freestyle Precision Pro Blood Glucose and β-Ketone Monitoring System
Regulation Name(s): Calculator/data processing module, for clinical use
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): Freestyle Precision Pro Blood Glucose and β-Ketone Meter
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Freestyle Precision Pro Blood Glucose and β-Ketone Monitoring System for quantitative measurement of glucose and β-ketone in whole blood samples in professional healthcare settings.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary, venous, arterial, and neonatal whole blood, and β-ketone in fresh capillary, venous, arterial, and neonatal whole blood (within 30 minutes), for multiple-patient use in professional healthcare settings as an aid to monitor effectiveness of diabetes control; not for diagnosis or screening of diabetes.
